{"tid":1811080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗：政府已高度戒備　毋須減往來武漢航班及高鐵班次","createTime":"2020-01-04T11:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T11:24:32.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"174a4abaf6843628fcf06e3683a1c1a3081b556e","tid":1811080,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:24:32.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗表示，政府已就武漢不明病毒性肺炎個案作出高度戒備，啟動嚴重應變級別，亦不斷與內地方面聯繫，強調不會掉以輕心，如出現爆發時可以即時回應。<br />\n<br />\n他又認為，最重要是防疫把關工作及注意個人衞生，現階段無必要減少來往武漢及香港的航班及高鐵班次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500981-20200104.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500981-20200104.htm&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=ed177995\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500981-20200104.htm&h=39f13be7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500981-20200104.htm</a>"}]}